metadata.name: DISTORTIONS #1
metadata.description:
Genesis piece of the DISTORTIONS series by BRAND. This is a unique 1/1 animation. Every single bidder on the initial auction will be airdropped an editioned (1/25) DISTORTIONS #2, #3, #4 or #5.

DISTORTIONS by BRAND is a series of 1/25 editioned animations and 1/1 unique animations. For sale in $ASH only. Available for sale and bidding 2022/02/22.
